# Nest & Whisk

Premium artisan cookie e-commerce platform built with Django.

## Dependency source of truth

This repository supports both of these install paths:

1. `requirements/dev.txt` for local development
2. `pyproject.toml` for metadata or editable installs

The runtime dependencies are intentionally mirrored in both places so `python manage.py check` works whether the environment was created from pip requirements or from project metadata.

## Quick start

```powershell
C:\Users\parag_bansal\PycharmProjects\Nest&Whisk\.venv\Scripts\python.exe -m pip install -r C:\Users\parag_bansal\PycharmProjects\Nest&Whisk\requirements\dev.txt
C:\Users\parag_bansal\PycharmProjects\Nest&Whisk\.venv\Scripts\python.exe C:\Users\parag_bansal\PycharmProjects\Nest&Whisk\manage.py check
```

## If your environment was installed from pyproject metadata

```powershell
C:\Users\parag_bansal\PycharmProjects\Nest&Whisk\.venv\Scripts\python.exe -m pip install -e C:\Users\parag_bansal\PycharmProjects\Nest&Whisk
C:\Users\parag_bansal\PycharmProjects\Nest&Whisk\.venv\Scripts\python.exe C:\Users\parag_bansal\PycharmProjects\Nest&Whisk\manage.py check
```

